<br>
BwT<br>
Can one still buy BwT in superior stores (sorry if this was answered elsewhere)?<br>
What's the lowest quality I can expect to find (I know this has been mentioned, but was unable to find it again) and what's the approximate req's for that?<br>
<br>
Pulling with bow<br>
